  "title": "ISic003512. I.Sicily inscription 003512",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλωδία Σε\n                    βῆρα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κλωδία\"><span data-text=\"Κλωδία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κλωδία\">Κλωδία</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Σε\n                    βῆρα\"><span data-text=\"Σε\n                    βῆρα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σεβῆρα\">Σε-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>βῆρα</span></span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησ\n                    σενἔζησεν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησ-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>σεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span> · <span data-text=\"ΙΙΠ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">Ι<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ι͡Π</span></span>´ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>❦ <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.6)</span> ❦ ❦ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. ΕΖΗΣ ΣΕΝἔζησ σεν</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Κλωδία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κλωδία\">Κλωδία</span>  <span data-text=\"Σεβῆρα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σεβῆρα\">Σεβῆρα</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησσεν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησσεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"ΙΙΠ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">ΙΙΠ</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.6)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κλωδία Σε\n                    βῆρα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κλωδία\"><span data-text=\"Κλωδία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κλωδία\">ΚΛΩΔΙΑ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Σε\n                    βῆρα\"><span data-text=\"Σε\n                    βῆρα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σεβῆρα\">ΣΕ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΒΗΡΑ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἔζησ\n                    σενἔζησεν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span>·<span data-text=\"ΙΙΠ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">Ι<span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">Ι͡Π</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>❦&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;❦❦</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.2 reg., orig. ΕΖΗΣ ΣΕΝἔζησ σεν</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Κλωδία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Κλωδία\">ΚΛΩΔΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Σεβῆρα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Σεβῆρα\">ΣΕΒΗΡΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησσεν\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ΙΙΠ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">ΙΙΠ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003512_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003512_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003512.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003512-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Bitto</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Klodia Sebera, lived 7 years</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The numeral is here interpreted (following Bitto) as acrophonic and ascending, i.e. two verticals, the second in ligature with a Π for πέντε. The hederae in the final line include a third hedera of different from.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1916 134 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701</a>  </li><li> Bitto 2001 5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>lunate epsilon, sigma and omega, ornate hederae.</p> Line 1-3  25  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
